data.description: This adorable two story home located in Winchester is ready for you to call it home! This property features PAID OFF SOLAR, a pool sized lot, water softener and LVP all throughout the home.  All 3 bedrooms are upstairs along with a small loft and full guest bath. The master bedroom features a large bathroom with dual sinks, separate toilet room and a walk in closet. This neighborhood is just minutes away from newer shopping centers, Lake Skinner & Temecula Wine Country. VERY LOW HOA!
